Syria to Appoint New Prime Minister in ‘Few Days,’ Watan Says

-- B y   L i n a   I b r a h i m
-- 
2011-03-30T05:47:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-30/syria-to-appoint-new-prime-minister-in-few-days-watan-says.html
Syria  will appoint a new prime
minister in a “few days,” Damascus-based Al Watan newspaper
reported, citing an unidentified official.  President Bashar al-Assad will give an “important speech
aimed at the Syrian people” today, the state-run SANA news
agency reported earlier today. Assad accepted Prime Minister
Muhammad Naji Otri’s resignation, state television reported
yesterday.  To contact the reporters on this story:  Lina Ibrahim in Dubai at 
 librahim4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Riad Hamade at 
 rhamade@bloomberg.net  